cs.SD, cs.SI, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.CL

The paper focuses on sound event detection using neural network frameworks and multiple instance learning. This falls under the intersection of signal processing (cs.SD) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.SI). The paper also addresses the problem of unbalanced datasets and co-occurrence of multiple categories, which relates to systems and control (cs.SY) and natural language processing (cs.CL).
